niceDesc: I had set off to the local marketplace early in the morning. Once I arrived, the usual hustle and bustle of the area had seemingly been replaced by lethargic, slow, and distracted patrons. Not terribly uncommon - on Coruscant you find many small-time celebrities who can bring most any area of the city to a standstill. Pushing my way through towards the clothing district, I was resolved not to be yet another blank-eyed fan. In my haste, I pushed with too much gusto. The resulting succession of tumbling bodies poured outward from me in all directions, knocking more than a few people off the causeway, towards their death below. In a blur of green, I felt something fly overhead. Before I realized it, those falling were saved. And then he looked at me and spoke one sentence  Hurry we must not. Muddled your mind becomes. A form of violence haste is. The dark side.
Author: LucasArts

Moments later I heard a yell, an explosion, and felt a hand grasp mine. Get up the voice yelled. We don t leave our own behind. I rose to my feet, and realized my salvation came at the hands of a man who looked no different then myself save for the brushes of blue upon his helmet. Never forget his heroism by purchasing a poster done in his honor.
